{"tid":988935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想知道港大候選內閣張信一識唔識講粵語/廣東話","createTime":"2019-01-20T13:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T00:13:57.000Z","uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbba4c9316478a924a26308d831e0238827a326e","tid":988935,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"成個訪問講英文咁搞笑？<br />\n粵語都唔識講點樣同學生有效溝通呢？<br />\n<br />\nCampus TV, HKUSU 香港大學學生會校園電視<br />\n<br />\n【專題訪問】2019年度香港大學學生會周年大選中央幹事會候選内閣蒼傲訪問（內務篇）<br />\n<br />\n中央幹事會候選內閣蒼傲就內務議題接受本台訪問，就內閣理念、參選原因、及政綱如增設中央幹事會席位專注管理國際生事務等發表意見<br />\n<br />\n訪問節錄如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 你們可否簡單自我介紹？<br />\n<br />\n鄭鎮熙（下稱鄭）：大家好我是鄭鎮熙（候選會長）， 來自理學院五年級。 今次參選學生會因為對學生會有一些意見、 一些改進空間、 自己一直以來都希望為學校和學校未來的發展而發出一些聲音。<br />\n<br />\n張信一（下稱張）：Hi I am Shun, studying Economics and Finance year 3. The main reason why i have nominated myself to be the executive committee of the HKUSU is because i have been a little bit unhappy with the way it has been running in the last few years i have been here. I want to see if I could make a difference....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkucampustv/?locale2=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2F%3Flocale2%3Dzh_HK&d=pNYsN7luP6RpznWW5VEjr7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=47a46ec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkucampustv/?locale2=zh_HK</a>"},{"pid":"f290a606035d666d92408ce42e383f0ef96c3f69","tid":988935,"uid":197852,"like":15,"dislike":16,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"反而唔係問題<br />\n因為hku is international school<br />\n你唔識英文反而比人笑<br />\n<br />\n問題係奶共"},{"pid":"9196cf59f9e98a1946933dedf22f4967cbe40e51","tid":988935,"uid":8883,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f290a606035d666d92408ce42e383f0ef96c3f69","tid":988935,"uid":197852,"like":15,"dislike":16,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"反而唔係問題<br />\n因為hku is international school<br />\n你唔識英文反而比人笑<br />\n<br